of arcbest corporationsm a transportation focused enterprise headquartered in fort smith arkansas arcbest technologies role is developing and supporting applications for the other subsidiaries in the arcbest corporate family we play an integral part in helping the other subsidiaries achieve their goals by providing innovative and uptodate information technology solutions to the business challenges they face arcbest technologies also provides comprehensive information services to a select group of noncorporate clients the largest subsidiary in the corporate family is abf freightsm a fortune  transportation and logistics supplier who has been recognized by receiving several awards of excellence abf freight is the only sixtime winner of the american trucking associations president�s trophy for safety and the only sixtime winner of the excellence in security award abf freight also is the only carrier to earn both the excellence in claimsloss prevention award and the excellence in security award in the same year which abf freight accomplished twice in  for the eighth consecutive year abf freight was ranked among the top  of selling power magazine�s listing of the  best us companies to sell for in the service sector abf freight was again the highestranking transportation company on the magazine�s  listing in  abf freight was also named one of training magazine�s training top  for the third consecutive year abf freight ranked seventh on the list vision the vision of arcbest technologies is to be a highly effective and respected information technology services provider the mission is to provide quality services in a costeffective manner to accomplish this arcbest technologies provides an outstanding hardware and system software environment one that has both the capacity and robustness needed by a major transportation company arcbest technologies next focuses on providing excellent customdeveloped software solutions that address the unique needs of abf freight and the other subsidiaries of arcbest corporation and finally arcbest technologies insures that access to its systems is fast efficient and secure utilizing the latest in system protection mechanisms and procedures arcbest technologies appreciates the strategic nature of information technology in business today and aims to provide not only technically effective applications but also applications that add genuine value to the overall business our role today over  employees of arcbest technologies provide a variety of services throughout the corporation and its other clients their primary function is designing programming and maintaining business application systems applications are developed for internet mainframe clientserver and personal computer environments applications include general business customer freight management human resources inventory management and control production control and demand forecasting equipment control and maintenance logistics imaging freight billing rating pricing and movement control management information reporting mobile computing systems barcoding electronic data interchange voice response systems careers learn more about the career opportunities at arcbest technologies internships arcbest technologies has an exciting and challenging summer internship program for it students privacy statement contact us   arcbest technologies inc all rights reserved subsidiary of arcbest corporation stock information  arcbest skip to main content × invalid login please try again menu arcbest corporation arcb nasdaq last price  days change   volume  low  high  investor contact david humphrey vice president investor relations p  f  dhumphreyarcbcom investor relations stock information stock information stock quote arcb      pm et on jul   previous close  open  volume  exchange nasdaq day high  day low  week high  week low  historical stock chart stock chart benchmark benchmark nasdaq nyse sp  amex compare area graph ohlc line graph candlestick time intraday  day 